{
  "stem": "17301.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 344.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no facilities in, in, you know, inside the car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave us buckets, you know, to relieve yourself, if you were able to, if you were able to get to it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or otherwise, there were old people and they just did what they had to do, without any help.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any food-- no food, none whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No water, no food, just like cattle, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't tell, nobody could tell what direction because there was no way of looking out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't look out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever there was, something that we could have, it was too high up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody could, you know, look that, that, high up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was like the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, if there is a little window that's very high up on the top, it's not in the middle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] When the train stopped and the doors opened, all we saw were men with striped clothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were, you know, just a shirt and pants, and a lot of German soldiers, a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they just surrounded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all I was hearing for them to say, macht schnell, macht schnell, to get off the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we jumped off, you know, right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, we didn't take anything with us because they told us, don't take anything with you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Leave everything on the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We left every, whatever we had, we left everything on the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then what happened-- they lined us up, and the men separate and the women separate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then what they did, the old people that were with young people went to one side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the healthy young girls or young mothers were going to another side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One was left and one was right.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
